description: Xull is an orcish legend in a game called Brawlhalla. Xull was the 35th legend and also the 1st legend having 9 points in one stat (strength), he uses a cannon and an axe. He was released November 22nd. After some time Xull got his visual rework however Iam NOT a fan of that rework!! Bring him back!
